container.title: Tutorials
container.description: Welcome to our Tutorials section. Here, you can find tutorials on various topics categorized for your convenience.

categories.name: SQL
categories.description: Learn the fundamentals of SQL, including queries, joins, and database design.

categories.name: NoSQL
categories.description: An introduction to NoSQL databases, covering different types like MongoDB, Cassandra, and Redis.

categories.name: Blockchain
categories.description: Explore the basics of blockchain technology, including how it works and its applications.

categories.name: Data Warehousing
categories.description: Understand the concepts of data warehousing, including ETL processes, data modeling, and reporting.

categories.name: Node.js
categories.description: Learn the fundamentals of Node.js, an open-source, cross-platform JavaScript runtime environment. This tutorial covers setting up Node.js, understanding the event-driven architecture, and building scalable network applications.

categories.name: Django
categories.description: Explore Django, a high-level Python web framework that encourages rapid development and clean, pragmatic design. This tutorial covers setting up a Django project, understanding the MVC architecture, and building dynamic web applications.

categories.name: FastAPI
categories.description: Delve into FastAPI, a modern, fast (high-performance) web framework for building APIs with Python 3.7+ based on standard Python type hints. This tutorial covers setting up FastAPI, creating endpoints, and implementing asynchronous request handling.

categories.name: Unity
categories.description: Learn how to create games using Unity, a powerful and widely-used game engine.

categories.name: Unreal Engine
categories.description: Explore game development with Unreal Engine, known for its high-quality graphics and performance.

categories.name: Godot Engine
categories.description: Discover the capabilities of Godot Engine, an open-source game engine that's easy to learn and use.

categories.name: CryEngine
categories.description: Dive into CryEngine for advanced game development with stunning visuals and powerful tools.

categories.name: GameMaker Studio
categories.description: Get started with GameMaker Studio, a great tool for creating 2D games quickly and efficiently.

categories.name: Construct
categories.description: Learn game development with Construct, a user-friendly engine perfect for creating HTML5 games.

categories.name: Roblox
categories.description: Create immersive experiences and games using Roblox, a platform beloved by millions of users worldwide.

categories.name: Artificial Intelligence
categories.description: An introduction to the concepts and applications of artificial intelligence, covering basic principles and real-world use cases.

categories.name: Machine Learning
categories.description: Learn the fundamentals of machine learning, including supervised and unsupervised learning, and how to implement algorithms in Python.

categories.name: Deep Learning
categories.description: A deep dive into neural networks and deep learning techniques, with hands-on examples using TensorFlow and Keras.

categories.name: OpenAI
categories.description: Get started with OpenAI's powerful AI models and tools. This tutorial covers integrating OpenAI's APIs, exploring capabilities like natural language processing and machine learning, and building intelligent applications using GPT models.

categories.name: R
categories.description: Comprehensive tutorials on R programming, focusing on data analysis, visualization, and statistical computing.

categories.name: MATLAB
categories.description: Learn MATLAB from basics to advanced applications, including mathematical modeling, simulation, and algorithm development.

categories.name: Linear Algebra
categories.description: Master the core concepts of Linear Algebra, including vectors, matrices, transformations, and eigenvalues—fundamental for machine learning, graphics, computer vision, and scientific computing.

categories.name: Discrete Mathematics
categories.description: Learn logic, set theory, combinatorics, graph theory, and proofs—critical for algorithms, data structures, databases, and security in computer science.

categories.name: Calculus
categories.description: Understand limits, derivatives, and integrals—essential for optimization, simulations, continuous models, and backpropagation in neural networks.

categories.name: Probability & Statistics
categories.description: Explore probability theory, distributions, hypothesis testing, and statistical inference—vital for AI, machine learning, analytics, and decision-making systems.

categories.name: Number Theory
categories.description: Dive into primes, modular arithmetic, and Diophantine equations—key to understanding cryptography, hashing, and secure communications.

categories.name: Differential Equations
categories.description: Study how to model change using differential equations—used in simulations, computer graphics, control systems, and deep learning architectures like Neural ODEs.

categories.name: Optimization
categories.description: Learn optimization techniques including linear programming, gradient descent, and convex analysis—crucial for training AI models, decision-making systems, and resource allocation in software engineering.
